text: Sára is a Hungarian and Czech female given name. Notable people with this name include: * Sándor Sára (1933–2019), Hungarian cinematographer and film director * Sára Bácskai (born 1999), Hungarian short track speed skater * Sára Cholnoky (born 1988), Hungarian sailor * Sára Jahodová, Czech curler * Sára Kaňkovská (born 1998), Czech racing cyclist * Sára Kovářová (born 1999), Czech handballer for DHK Baník Most and the Czech national team * Sára Nysted (born 2001), Faroese swimmer * Sára Pusztai, Hungarian football player * Sára Salkaházi (1899–1944), Hungarian nun * Sára Szenteleki-Ligetkuti (born 1945), Hungarian middle-distance runner * Sára Tóth (born 1993), Hungarian handball player * Sára Vybíralová (born 1986), Czech writer ==See also== * Sarah (given name)
title: Sára
